"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-is-simone-biles-dealing-with-ankle-injury-2024-olympics-live-updates\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"After Simone Biles finished up her balance beam routine on Sunday, she appeared to suffer a possible injury to her ankle.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It seemed as if the ailment was bothering her during warmups for the floor exercise routine.\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 214, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As Biles got on the mat to perform her ground routine, her left ankle/lower leg was wrapped, and she came off the mat after completing her performance appearing to walk somewhat gingerly on that leg.\", \"from\": 216, \"to\": 415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She sat at a chair with her leg pulled up.\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 458, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her routine\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the same one she performed at qualification a month ago\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094did not appear overly impacted by the injury, a display of toughness from the seven-time Olympic medal athlete.\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 643, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During springboard warmups, after she took a warmup jump, she crawled back to her teammates, then got up and jumped on her good leg for several steps, a sight that would have been greater cause for concern had Biles not been laughing while she did it.\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 896, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Later, she attempted a double pike during warmups and did not land it cleanly.\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 976, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Afterward, broadcasts showed her hitting a foam roller on the calf area of the left leg.\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After landing her double pike vault, she let out a \\\"yay\\\" that cameras caught.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She did not fall.\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She scored a 15.8 (6.400 difficulty, 9.400 execution, 0.00 penalty).\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1231, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her second vault she also landed, scoring 14.800 (5.600 difficulty, 9.200 execution, 0.00 penalty) She limped off the stage stairs despite the solid score and quality execution that showed little to no impact from the injury.\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles performed well on the uneven bars and came off with a massive smile and plenty of applause.\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1557, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The team said they do not think the injury is going to be serious but will take a closer look at the injury she fought through in qualification.\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Afterwards, coach Cecile Landile said there is no discussion of Biles withdrawing.\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s injury is a minor calf issue from a couple of weeks ago that flared up during floor warmups, according to her coach, Cecile Landi.\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1936, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There was no discussion of her withdrawing from the competition.\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 2001, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations  Josh Wilson is the news director of the Breaking and Trending News team at Sports Illustrated.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2094, \"end\": 2098, \"title\